
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor BO as Business Owner
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant CP as Control Plane
  participant PDP as Policy (PDP)
  participant DB as Postgres
  BO->>UI: Submit use case intake form
  UI->>CP: POST /v1/use_cases
  CP->>PDP: authorize(action=use_case.create)
  PDP-->>CP: ALLOW
  CP->>DB: Create UseCase + initial RiskTier + owners
  CP-->>UI: UseCase created (score pending)
  Note over CP: Optional async scoring + reviewers assignment
